The company 1 - 800 - GOT - JUNK ? , based in Vancouver , Canada , operates in North American and International franchise locations . The company removes and recycles various wastes while also providing cleanup services for industries such as property management and construction . The 18 year old entrepreneur was inspired to open the business after seeing a junk hauling truck in front of him at a McDonald 's Drive - thru . 1 - 800 - GOT - JUNK ? was originally named the Rubbish Boys and grew to be the largest junk removal service in Vancouver , British Columbia . The company changed names in 1998 and began franchising in 1999 , opening locations in Toronto , Ontario and Portland , Oregon . They have since grown to more than 260 locations throughout the US , Canada , Australia , and the UK . 